Pendulum Effect
 When you Pendulum Summon a Zombie-Type monster(s): You can activate this effect; this turn, they cannot be destroyed by battle or by card effects.

 Monster Effect
 If this card destroys an opponent's monster by battle: You can target 1 Pendulum Monster in your Graveyard; add it to your hand.
